								</li>
								<li class="">HIGH NET WORTH INDIVIDUALS
									<Icon primary="w-8 group-hover:text-orange text-gray-950" path="M17.25 8.25 21 12m0 0-3.75 3.75M21 12H3" />
								</li>
								<li class="">INTERNATIONAL DIVORCE CASES
									<Icon primary="w-8 group-hover:text-orange text-gray-950" path="M17.25 8.25 21 12m0 0-3.75 3.75M21 12H3" />
								</li>
								<li class="">FAMILY BUSINESSES & SELF-EMPLOYED
									<Icon primary="w-8 group-hover:text-orange text-gray-950" path="M17.25 8.25 21 12m0 0-3.75 3.75M21 12H3" />
